    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-03-09T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-03-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="253"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d253">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">840.48 Refugees/3649</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Polish Ambassador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Ciechanowski</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Ambassador of Poland presents his compliments to the Secretary of State and
                    acting upon instructions of his Government has the honor to give the Government
                    of the United States an assurance to the effect that all Polish citizens who
                    became refugees as a result of the war and found or are finding refuge on the
                    territory of the United States of America, will be readmitted to Poland after
                    the war when conditions permit and no obstacles will be placed in the way of
                    their return by the Polish Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-09">March 9,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                    <lb/> No. 738/SZ–202. </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
